data.description: Beautiful two-story home situated on 1.2 acres. Now available in Riverview Pointe! Immerse yourself in the southern lifestyle with this 4-bedroom, three and a half bath house that has something for everyone just minutes away from Dog River and the Mobile Yacht Club. Step inside and be greeted by a dramatic entrance with soaring ceilings. The welcoming bright and open living room is perfect for entertaining guests or enjoying quality time with your family. This home boasts 9ft ceilings, an open floor plan, formal dining room and cozy family room with a gas fireplace. Two bonus rooms provide a wide range of opportunities for your family's enjoyment. Prepare to be mesmerized by the breathtaking sunsets visible from the upper level and outdoor living space, where you can relax and indulge in your private backyard featuring a screened in patio, oversized deck and an inground pool which has an all-new pump and new liner replaced in Feb 2023! Updates include, two new hot water heaters, new pool sand filter, pool pump, pool liner & new septic pump. One year home warranty to be provided. Embrace the outdoor experience by engaging in friendly games of corn hole or lounging in the hammock while savoring your favorite cocktail. For fishing enthusiasts, this property offers use of fishing pond and fishing opportunities of the nearby river coast. Parking and storage are not an issue with plenty of space available including a custom outdoor storage building. Your dream of owning a slice of paradise can become a reality! Schedule a private tour today! NOTE*****Seller to contribute $5000 towards Buyers Closing Costs & Pre-Paid Items!
